    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/fulgor-milano/">Fulgor Milano brand hub</a> · <a href="/brands/fulgor-milano-stove-repair/">Fulgor Milano range / stove</a> · <a href="/brands/ilve-range-hood-repair/">ILVE range hood (Italian peer)</a> · <a href="/brands/bertazzoni-range-hood-repair/">Bertazzoni range hood (Italian peer)</a> · <a href="/services/range-hood-repair/">Range hood repair (service hub)</a> · <a href="/commercial/exhaust-hood-repair/">Commercial exhaust hood repair</a>. For commercial kitchen exhaust hood repair (restaurant/foodservice Captive-Aire, Halton scope), see our <a href="/commercial/exhaust-hood-repair/">commercial page</a>.</p>
